a&quot;,&quot;Huawei Technologies&quot;,&quot;Ciena Corporation&quot;,&quot;Infinera Corporation&quot;,&quot;Juniper Networks&quot;,&quot;Arista Networks&quot;,&quot;Broadcom Inc.&quot;,&quot;Xilinx (a AMD company)&quot;,&quot;Keysight Technologies&quot;]"><meta name="intent_signals" content="[&quot;Interest in advanced optical transmitter testing methods&quot;,&quot;Seeking information on TDECQ as a performance metric for PAM4 transmitters&quot;,&quot;Looking to understand the advantages of TDECQ over TDP and traditional tests&quot;,&quot;Desire to implement or improve testing procedures using sampling oscilloscopes&quot;,&quot;Evaluating the correlation between TDECQ measurements and real system performance&quot;]"><meta name="related_topics" content="[&quot;Advanced Techniques for PAM4 Signal Equalization and Noise Management&quot;,&quot;Comparison of TDECQ and TDP Metrics in Optical Transmitter Testing&quot;,&quot;Impact of Receiver Equalization on TDECQ Measurements and System Performance&quot;,&quot;Standards and Future Developments in PAM4 Optical Communication Systems&quot;,&quot;Practical Implementation of TDECQ Testing in Manufacturing Environments&quot;]"><meta name="job_functions" content="[&quot;Optical Communications Engineer&quot;,&quot;Test and Measurement Engineer&quot;,&quot;Optical Transmitter Design Engineer&quot;,&quot;Systems Engineer (Optical Systems)&quot;,&quot;Fiber Optic Network Engineer&quot;,&quot;Research and Development Engineer (Optical Technologies)&quot;,&quot;Hardware Validation Engineer&quot;,&quot;Signal Integrity Engineer&quot;,&quot;Product Development Engineer (Optical Components)&quot;,&quot;Quality Assurance Engineer (Optical Systems)&quot;]"><meta name="bcCatalog" content="internalEditorial"><meta name="BlueConic" content="{&quot;page_type&quot;:&quot;content&quot;,&quot;canonical_path&quot;:&quot;/technologies/test-measurement/article/21283812/keysight-technologies-tdecq-understanding-the-theory-behind-the-key-metric-for-p