<!----><div class="ebm-page__primary"><div class="grid" style="max-width:1300px;padding-top:0;margin-top:0;" data-v-c8b9d79e><!--[--><div class="web-row grid-row hide-bottom-border always" style="margin-bottom:var(--client-spacing);" data-v-c8b9d79e data-v-196964cf><!----><div class="row-1 row layoutundefined site-width" style="border-top:;background-color:white;color:black;border-radius:0;margin-bottom:0;box-shadow:;gap:var(--client-spacing);padding:0;" data-v-196964cf><!--[--><div style="padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;" class="column-wrapper" data-v-196964cf><div style="width:100%;" data-v-196964cf><div class="column-1 column block-align-top" data-v-196964cf data-v-beab612a><div class="standard-blocks" style="display:flex;flex:1 0 100%;align-items:stretch;" data-v-beab612a><!--[--><div class="block-wrapper 1787-855f-3dc-24c5 hide-bottom-border" style="margin-bottom:0;padding-top:0;display:flex;flex:1 0 100%;align-items:stretch;" data-v-beab612a><div class="block-1 block" data-v-beab612a data-v-94d9b856><div class="above-cta" style="background-color:white;border:;padding:0;border-radius:0;box-shadow:;" data-v-94d9b856><!----><div class="content" style="border-radius:0;padding:0px;" data-v-94d9b856><div style="min-height:0;" class="gam-slot-builder" block-id="1787-855f-3dc-24c5" data-v-94d9b856><div class="ebm-ad-target__outer" style="min-height:0;min-width:300px;"><span></span></div></div></div></div><!----></div></div><!--]--></div><!----></div></div></div><!--]--></div></div><div class="web-row grid-row always" style="margin-bottom:0;" data-v-c8b9d79e data-v-196964cf><!----><div class="row-2 row layout2_1 largest_first site-width" style="border-top:;background-color:#ffffff;color:black;border-radius:0;margin-bottom:0;box-shadow:;gap:var(--client-spacing);padding:0;" data-v-196964cf><!--[--><div style="padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;" class="column-wrapper" data-v-196964cf><div style="width:100%;" data-v-196964cf><div class="column-1 column block-align-top" data-v-196964cf data-v-beab612a><div class="standard-blocks" style="display:block;flex:;align-items:;" data-v-beab612a><!--[--><div class="block-wrapper e584-71c9-8f3-5010" style="margin-bottom:24px;padding-top:0;display:block;flex:;align-items:;" data-v-beab612a><div class="block-1 block" data-v-beab612a data-v-94d9b856><div class="above-cta" style="background-color:white;border:;padding:0;border-radius:0;box-shadow:;" data-v-94d9b856><!----><div class="content" style="border-radius:0;padding:0px;" data-v-94d9b856><div class="web-content-title-new left" block-id="e584-71c9-8f3-5010" data-v-94d9b856><div class="above-line" role="region"><div class="section-wrapper left"><div><!--[--><a href="/technologies/test-measurement" class="section">Test &amp; Measurement</a><!--]--></div><!----></div><h1 class="title-text">TDECQ: Understanding the Theory Behind the Key Metric for PAM4 Optical Transmitters</h1><div class="teaser-text">When decisions were made to change from historical NRZ or simple on-off modulation to PAM4 in the development of advanced comms systems, methods to quantify transmitter performance needed to be created. Enter TDECQ. </div><div class="byline-event-group"><!----><div class="author-row"><!----><div class="all-authors"><div class="author-contributor"><!--[--><div class="author"><div><!--[--><a href="/21810006">Greg Le Cheminant</a><!--]--></div><!----></div><!--]--></div><div class="company-link">Related To:  <div><!--[--><a href="/21146158">Keysight Technologies</a><!--]--></div></div></div><div class="dot first"></div><div class="date-read-time"><div class="date">March 1, 2024</div><div class="dot second"></div><div class="read-time">10 min read </div></div></div><div class="ebm-button-wrapper icon hollow google-button" style="--button-text-color:var(--color-white);--button-accent-color:#868686;--hollow-hover-background:#d9d9d9;" data-v-ab2fac35><a href="https://www.google.com/preferences/source?q=electronicdesign.com" class="ebm-button ebm-button--hollow ebm-button--small" target="_blank" style="border-radius:0;" data-v-ab2fac35><div class="content icon-left" data-v-ab2fac35><!--[--><div class="ebm-icon mdi:plus-box-multiple-outline" style="min-width:18px;min-height:18px;color:;" data-v-ab2fac35><span class="iconify i-mdi:plus-box-multiple-outline icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:18px;color:;"></span> </div><span class="ebm-button-label" data-v-ab2fac35>Add Us On Google</span><!--]--><!----></div></a></div></div></div><div class="below-line"><div class="comment-count"><div style="display:none;"><span></span></div></div><div class="ebm-share-wrapper" role="region" content-id="21283812" data-v-feabd68e><ul class="ebm-share-list" data-v-feabd68e><!--[--><li class="ebm-share-item facebook-icon" data-v-feabd68e><a href="javascript:void(0)" aria-label="facebook" data-v-feabd68e><!--[--><div class="ebm-icon mingcute:facebook-line" style="min-width:20px;min-height:20px;color:#868686;" data-v-feabd68e><span class="iconify i-mingcute:facebook-line icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:20px;color:#868686;"></span> </div><!--]--></a></li><li class="ebm-share-item linkedin-icon" data-v-feabd68e><a href="javascript:void(0)" aria-label="linkedin" data-v-feabd68e><!--[--><div class="ebm-icon mingcute:linkedin-line" style="min-width:20px;min-height:20px;color:#868686;" data-v-feabd68e><span class="iconify i-mingcute:linkedin-line icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:20px;color:#868686;"></span> </div><!--]--></a></li><li class="ebm-share-item twitter-icon" data-v-feabd68e><a href="javascript:void(0)" aria-label="twitter" data-v-feabd68e><!--[--><div class="ebm-icon mingcute:social-x-line" style="min-width:20px;min-height:20px;color:#868686;" data-v-feabd68e><span class="iconify i-mingcute:social-x-line icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:20px;color:#868686;"></span> </div><!--]--></a></li><li class="ebm-share-item reddit-icon" data-v-feabd68e><a href="javascript:void(0)" aria-label="reddit" data-v-feabd68e><!--[--><div class="ebm-icon mingcute:reddit-line" style="min-width:20px;min-height:20px;color:#868686;" data-v-feabd68e><span class="iconify i-mingcute:reddit-line icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:20px;color:#868686;"></span> </div><!--]--></a></li><!--]--><li class="ebm-share-item email-icon" data-v-feabd68e><a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#" aria-label="email" data-v-feabd68e><div class="ebm-icon mdi:email-outline" style="min-width:20px;min-height:20px;color:#868686;" data-v-feabd68e><span class="iconify i-mdi:email-outline icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:20px;color:#868686;"></span> </div></a></li></ul></div><div class="print-favorite" role="region"><div><!--[--><a href="/print/content/21283812" target="_blank" aria-label="print"><div class="ebm-icon mdi:printer-outline" style="min-width:20px;min-height:20px;color:#868686;"><span class="iconify i-mdi:printer-outline icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:20px;color:#868686;"></span> </div></a><!--]--></div><!----></div></div><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----></div></div><div class="block-wrapper 2d01-2332-aa0-cf33" style="margin-bottom:24px;padding-top:24px;display:block;flex:;align-items:;" data-v-beab612a><div class="block-2 block" data-v-beab612a data-v-94d9b856><div class="above-cta" style="background-color:white;border:;padding:0;border-radius:0;box-shadow:;" data-v-94d9b856><!----><div class="content" style="border-radius:0;padding:0px;" data-v-94d9b856><div class="ebm-content-teaser-image" style="width:100%;" block-id="2d01-2332-aa0-cf33" data-v-94d9b856><span class="ebm-content-teaser-image__small"><div class="web-image" credit-position="top"><figure class="ebm-image-wrapper"><div class="image-credit" data-v-ab10a904><div class="text-wrapper" data-v-ab10a904><div class="text" style="font-family:Inter;" data-v-ab10a904>Dreamstime_agsandrew_32581249</div></div><div class="icon-wrapper" data-v-ab10a904><div class="ebm-icon mdi:image-area icon" style="min-width:16px;min-height:16px;color:;" data-v-ab10a904><span class="iconify i-mdi:image-area icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;color:;"></span> </div></div></div><div href target="_blank" aria-label class="ebm-image -type container" style="padding:0;"><div class="image-content"><div src="https://img.electronicdesign.com/files/base/ebm/electronicdesign/image/2024/03/65e1fbaf709a66001eb9fdd7-dreamstime_agsandrew_32581249promo.png?auto=format,compress&amp;fit=fill&amp;fill=blur&amp;q=45?w=250&amp;width=250" alt="65e1fbaf709a66001eb9fdd7 Dreamstime Agsandrew 32581249promo" height width="250" title="65e1fbaf709a66001eb9fdd7 Dreamstime Agsandrew 32581249promo"><img src="https://img.electronicdesign.com/files/base/ebm/electronicdesign/image/2024/03/65e1fbaf709a66001eb9fdd7-dreamstime_agsandrew_32581249promo.png?auto=format,compress&fit=fill&fill=blur&q=45?w=250&width=250" alt="65e1fbaf709a66001eb9fdd7 Dreamstime Agsandrew 32581249promo" height="" width="250" title="65e1fbaf709a66001eb9fdd7 Dreamstime Agsandrew 32581249promo" loading="lazy" width="250" height="" style="border-radius: 0" /></div></div><!----></div></figure></div></span><!----><!----><!----></div></div></div><!----></div></div><div class="block-wrapper 766fd320-b9de-417c-aff3-7aec24dd1b6a hide-bottom-border" style="margin-bottom:24px;padding-top:24px;display:block;flex:;align-items:;" data-v-beab612a><div class="block-3 block" data-v-beab612a data-v-94d9b856><div class="above-cta" style="background-color:white;border:;padding:0;border-radius:0;box-shadow:;" data-v-94d9b856><!----><div class="content" style="border-radius:0;padding:0px;" data-v-94d9b856><div class="body-block" block-id="766fd320-b9de-417c-aff3-7aec24dd1b6a" data-v-94d9b856><div id="before-content"></div><div class="body-content"><!----><div><!--[--><div type="style"><style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100..900&display=swap');
