796},{"id":797,"thumbnail":798,"description":799,"published":800,"title":801,"url":802},"0q77OtFeUX8","https:\u002F\u002Fi.ytimg.com\u002Fvi\u002F0q77OtFeUX8\u002Fsddefault.jpg","Watch this quick video to explore the new features of our product pages – designed for speed and technical clarity. See how we deliver critical product data upfront, utilize icons for rapid comprehension, and offer an enhanced live Chat system for expert support.",1777398217000,"Master Bond Product Pages","https:\u002F\u002Fyoutu.be\u002F0q77OtFeUX8",{"node":804},{"id":805,"thumbnail":806,"description":807,"published":808,"title":809,"url":810},"7_R6vm9-lgM","https:\u002F\u002Fi.ytimg.com\u002Fvi\u002F7_R6vm9-lgM\u002Fsddefault.jpg","See how Master Bond and Nordson collaborated to solve a critical manufacturing challenge in wearable sensor production. By combining Master Bond’s pre-mixed and frozen two-part epoxy compound with Nordson’s precision automated dispensing system, the integrated approach eliminated the formation of air bubbles during application—delivering consistent, void-free encapsulation and greater process reliability.",1770220783000,"Encapsulating Wearable Sensors with Two-Part Epoxy","https:\u002F\u002Fyoutu.be\u002F7_R6vm9-lgM",{"node":812},{"id":813,"thumbnail":814,"description":815,"published":816,"title":817,"url":818},"qaNo2Q5vA3U","https:\u002F\u002Fi.ytimg.com\u002Fvi\u002FqaNo2Q5vA3U\u002Fsddefault.jpg","Product reliability starts with the right bond. Master Bond delivers high-performance epoxy, silicone, and UV-curable adhesive systems backed by expert technical support. From prototype to full production, we’re your engineering partner.",1769705419000,"Master Bond | High-Performance Adhesives","https:\u002F\u002Fyoutu.be\u002FqaNo2Q5vA3U",{"alias":820,"name":821},"directory\u002Fmaterials-packaging\u002Fadhesives","Adhesives",{"path":823},"\u002Fdirectory\u002Fmaterials-packaging\u002Fadhesives\u002Fcompany\u002F21240172\u002Fmaster-bond",[825,828,833,837,842,844,